# vfs_io: PR 6b's `vfs open` + `vfs getline` engine surface.
# Reuses the .tree/ + {ROOT} substitution harness from PR 5/6a.
#
# Coverage:
#   - open of a file dentry returns "ok: <content>"
#   - open of a directory dentry returns "err: other" (IoError.other
#     "is a directory")
#   - getline on each line index returns "some: <line>"
#   - getline past EOF returns "none"
#   - getline against a directory dentry (open fails) returns "none"
vfs register fs {ROOT} mounted
vfs walk 0 b.txt
vfs walk 0 lines.txt
vfs open 1
vfs open 2
vfs getline 2 0
vfs getline 2 1
vfs getline 2 2
vfs getline 2 99
vfs open 0
vfs getline 0 0
